ShinyHelper-package     Making shiny application creation easier
checkboxGroupArrayInput
                        Checkbox Group Input Control (Array Layout)
createApp               Create the Shiny application from the
                        accumulated objects
epi                     2012 Environmental Performance Index Data
headerPanelAdd          Create a header panel
injectData              Inject a data set into the Shiny application
                        under construction
numericInputAdd         Create a numeric input control
plotOutputAdd           Create an plot output element
selectInputAdd          Create a select list input control
shinySkeleton           Create a skeleton for a Shiny application
showUI                  Convenience functions for the Shiny application
                        creation process
sliderInputAdd          Slider Input Widget
textInputAdd            Create a text input control
